  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nMetaverse Nomads #130 Star Atlas Stress Test Review\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nStar Atlas Throwdown: SCORE VS SAGE (part 2)\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of part 2 of his SCORE versus SAGE training series.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #113\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas Throwdown!: SCORE VS SAGE (Part 3)\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of part 3 of his SCORE versus SAGE training series.\nAtlas Brew #96\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas: SCORE VS SAGE – Lab Assistant Tutorial\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video tutorial of the Lab Assistant tool.\nStar Atlas RECAP – Atlas Brew #96 w/ the ECON Team\nRahMega posted a video recap of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas Community Week: A Galactic Celebration\nStar Atlas published an article about the upcoming Community Week.\nSTAR ATLAS #218 An Intruder, Giant Announcement & Automation!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video recap of latest Star Atlas news.\nPress Release: The Council of Peace Assembly (COPA) Returns for Its Second Edition\nStar Atlas published an article about an upcoming Star Atlas event.",
